    "为什么不能替你建:『信息』自动化能在锁屏、你不在场时读到整条短信,iOS 出于隐私保护,规定这一步只能你亲手在「快捷指令」app 里建。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Why we can't create it for you: a Messages automation can read your full message even on the lock screen while you're away. For privacy, iOS requires that you create this step yourself in the Shortcuts app."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "为什么不能替你建:『信息』自动化能在锁屏、你不在场时读到整条短信,iOS 出于隐私保护,规定这一步只能你亲手在「快捷指令」app 里建。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "为什么要你亲手建:iOS 出于隐私,自动化只能你自己在「快捷指令」app 里建,任何 app 都无法替你创建。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Why you build it yourself: for privacy, iOS only lets you create automations yourself in the Shortcuts app — no app can create one for you."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "为什么要你亲手建:iOS 出于隐私,自动化只能你自己在「快捷指令」app 里建,任何 app 都无法替你创建。"
          }
        }
