    "有些银行/平台只发交易邮件,不发短信。配一次「邮件」自动化,以后每来一封交易邮件都会自动识别成一笔待确认。下面带你建这唯一一次自动化。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Some banks/platforms only send transaction emails, not SMS. Set up an “Email” automation once, and every transaction email after that is automatically turned into a draft for confirmation. We’ll walk you through this one-time setup."
