    "若同一笔也来了银行短信或已用 Apple Pay 记过,app 会在待确认收件箱把后到的那条标记为「可能重复」,你拒绝即可,绝不会重复算两笔(除非确属两笔)。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If the same purchase also arrives by bank SMS or was already recorded via Apple Pay, the app flags the later one as “possibly duplicate” in the inbox — just reject it. It never double-counts (unless they really are two purchases)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "若同一笔也来了银行短信或已用 Apple Pay 记过,app 会在待确认收件箱把后到的那条标记为「可能重复」,你拒绝即可,绝不会重复算两笔(除非确属两笔)。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "若某笔同时收到了银行短信,app 会在待确认收件箱把那条短信草稿标记为「可能与 Apple Pay 重复」,你拒绝即可,绝不会重复算两笔(除非确属两笔)。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If a payment also triggers a bank SMS, the app flags that SMS draft in the pending inbox as a possible Apple Pay duplicate — just reject it; you'll never be double-counted (unless they really are two purchases)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "若某笔同时收到了银行短信,app 会在待确认收件箱把那条短信草稿标记为「可能与 Apple Pay 重复」,你拒绝即可,绝不会重复算两笔(除非确属两笔)。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
